                    <div style="font-size:0.78rem; font-weight:700; color:#16a34a; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">✅ HEALTHY STOCK — STARS</div>
                    <div style="font-size:0.72rem; color:#15803d; line-height:1.5;">
                        BLACKSERIES (11 wk), METALIC (20 wk), ONYX (37 wk) — stok cukup untuk Stars. Pastikan tidak ada stockout di warna-warna populer. BLACKSERIES paling kritis — monitor weekly.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div style="background:#002A3A; border-radius:8px; padding:1rem; color:white;">
                    <div style="font-size:0.72rem; line-height:1.6; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">
                        💡 <strong style="color:#00E273;">OTB Opportunity:</strong> Clearance Dogs series (FLO, ELSA, PUFFY, <strong style="color:#f87171;">AIRMOVE, LUCA, LUNA</strong>) = ~57K+ units. Airmove+Luca+Luna saja: 25.5K units, est. nilai ~Rp 5–7B. Jika sold at 40–50% discount → recovered cash ~Rp 3–3.5B untuk reinvest ke Stars. Priority clearance: LUNA (104wk), LUCA (90wk) → paling critical.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footnote">Stock = mart.sku_portfolio (stok_global). WoS = stok_global ÷ (pairs_ytd / 7 minggu). Target ideal: 8–16 weeks. >26wk = at risk. LUNA: 104wk, LUCA: 90wk, AIRMOVE: 41wk — ketiganya extreme overstock jauh di atas threshold 26wk. Data diupdate Feb 2026 review.</div>
</div>

